window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>An all-new <b>small town friends to lovers suspense romance </b>from a <i>USA Today </i>bestselling author and performed by Robert Hatchet, Kelli Lindsay, and Tyler Darby.</p> <p>I’m not in the habit of kissing strangers, especially sexy ones. But when my jealous ex comes looking for me, fake-flirting with a handsome city slicker seems like the perfect solution.</p> <p>If only the stranger’s kiss didn’t leave me panting, and if only I hadn’t ended up agreeing to be a tour guide for him and his best friend.</p> <p>I don’t have time to coddle two clueless billionaires in the wilderness, not when my family’s land is being threatened by a shady development scheme. I need all my energy and resources to fight.</p> <p>But the more time I spend with these two hunky best friends, the closer we become. Our harmless teasing turns reckless, until we’re sharing our deepest fantasies and breaking our own rules.</p> <p>Until the truth reveals a betrayal so deep, I'm faced with an impossible choice: protect what I love, or surrender to my heart.</p> <p><i>If you like spice and suspense, you’ll devour Dakota’s sexy small town romance.</i></p> <p><b>Scroll up to start listening to this powerful love story today!</b></p> <p><i>♥ This is book 5 in the Wild Hearts small town romantic suspense series featuring the fierce-loving McCabe family. Lexie's story features some playful MFM why choose moments but ends with MF. It can be enjoyed as a stand-alone but most have preferred exploring the books in order ♥</i></p>"; 
